### Health check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

###

### Get all workouts (kaikki päivät)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/workouts

###

### Get specific day's workout (tietyn päivän treeni)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/workouts/2025-10-20

###

### Add exercise to a day (lisää liike päivään)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/workouts/2025-10-20/exercises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Penkkipunnerrus",
  "sets": 4,
  "reps": 10,
  "weight": 80
}

###

### Update workout type for a day (vaihda päivän treenityyppi)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/workouts/2025-10-20/type
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workoutType": "Työntö"
}

###

### Toggle exercise completion (merkkaa liike tehdyksi/ei-tehdyksi)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/workouts/2025-10-20/exercises/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

###

### Delete exercise (poista liike)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/workouts/2025-10-20/exercises/1

